data.description: Welcome to Winterset!  This beautiful 1 owner home built in 2019 sits on a quiet cul-de-sac on the edge of town. The Primary bedroom includes a full bathroom leading to a large walk-in closet. All 4 bedrooms are placed throughout the spacious hallway found on the 2nd level. The roomy kitchen includes a pantry and plenty of counter space to enjoy cooking, and then serving meals in the formal dining area. The backyard is perfect for entertaining guests, with the full outdoor kitchen, and space for playing yard games!  Don’t miss this opportunity!  Schedule a showing today.  All information obtained from seller and public records.
